Package: abds
Title: Datasets for 'The Biologist's R'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mohamed", "Jumanne",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "author@abds.science",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: A collection of synthetic but ecologically realistic datasets
    designed to accompany 'The Biologist's R: A Practical Introduction to
    Data Analysis for Field Scientists' by Mohamed Jumanne (Applied
    Bio-Data Science, 2026). All datasets represent insect survey data
    from a fictional tropical landscape and are structured to teach
    progressive analytical skills from data import through to generalised
    linear modelling. Datasets are suitable for teaching R, ecological
    statistics, and reproducible research practices.
